                <p><strong>Brainstorming (45-90 minutes):</strong> Encourage wild ideas first, then refine and prioritize solutions.</p>
                <p><strong>Status reviews (30-45 minutes):</strong> Focus on exceptions and blockers, not routine updates that could be shared asynchronously.</p>
                
